the fun of having to build a
robot.

31:57.816 --> 32:03.488 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: And why ask about
money? Because,
here, kids get paid for
achievements through

32:03.522 --> 32:07.726 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
