Raise.me.

32:07.759 --> 32:09.661 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Senior Barbara Groh:

32:09.694 --> 32:13.231 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARBARA GROH, Student: They call
them micro-scholarships,
and it's all based on your
portfolio, your

32:13.265 --> 32:13.765 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
profile.

32:13.799 --> 32:15.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
PAUL SOLMAN: Right.

32:15.534 --> 32:18.537 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARBARA GROH: So, for different
aspects of
my profile, I can get different
amounts of

32:18.570 --> 32:21.306 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
