more money.

33:13.525 --> 33:18.430 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: More money for
immediate achievements,
says Raise.me's founder Preston
Silverman.

33:18.463 --> 33:23.802 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PRESTON SILVERMAN, Founder,
Raise.me: Instead
of waiting for four years to
find out if you're

33:23.835 --> 33:28.840 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
going to receive any
scholarship, students
are getting a short feedback
loop each semester,

33:28.874 --> 33:30.642 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
