33:30.675 --> 33:32.377 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANEESH RAMAN, Raise.me: It's a
huge pool of
money that colleges are giving
out to kids

33:32.410 --> 33:36.314 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
after they have applied, after
they have gotten
in, now goes to kids starting as
early as

33:36.348 --> 33:37.983 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
ninth grade.

33:38.016 --> 33:41.519 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: Yes, it only goes
