33:45.390 --> 33:48.927 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANEESH RAMAN: It motivates them
to do better
in high school and it prepares
them better

33:48.960 --> 33:53.665 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
for college, so, when they go,
they actually
finish, get a diploma, find a
job, live the

33:53.698 --> 33:55.433 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
American dream. That's the idea.

33:55.467 --> 34:00.405 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: Senior Sabrina
Rosell is one
of Terra's typically high
achievers. But,

34:00.438 --> 34:07.045 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
like almost all the students
