has four siblings.

34:16.421 --> 34:19.791 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SABRINA ROSELL, Student: It may
look like
my family doesn't qualify for
financial aid,

34:19.824 --> 34:23.795 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
