thus far represents a fair chunk
of that tuition.

34:29.334 --> 34:33.505 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SABRINA ROSELL: It's just like
-- almost like
a gift in exchange for all of
our hard work.

34:33.538 --> 34:35.440 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: Rosell's fellow
students agree.

34:35.473 --> 34:39.477 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUSTIN LEE, Student: I finally
found out something
that I can get from working
hard, besides

34:39.511 --> 34:41.880 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
just the good feeling from
working hard, you
know?

34:41.913 --> 34:46.017 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: But if the students
at Terra
don't need the motivational
nudge of financial

34:46.051 --> 34:52.424 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
