the money, students
elsewhere seriously need both,
says Raise.me

34:52.457 --> 34:54.192 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
founder Silverman.

34:54.225 --> 34:57.595 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PRESTON SILVERMAN: We spend
almost all of
our time reaching out to schools
and school

34:57.629 --> 35:03.234 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
