35:09.407 --> 35:11.176 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WOMAN: How many of you want to
go to college?

35:11.209 --> 35:12.978 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
(CHEERING AND APPLAUSE)

35:13.011 --> 35:17.882 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: OK, so, next
morning, we joined
a Raise.me reach-out rally at a
distinctly

35:17.916 --> 35:20.618 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
