High.

35:20.652 --> 35:25.657 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN: OK. Let's take some guesses
on how you
much you can earn for different
things on

35:25.690 --> 35:29.527 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Raise. Everyone who answers
right, we will
give you a prize.

35:29.561 --> 35:36.001 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
How much do you guys think you
can get for
getting an A or a B in class?

35:36.034 --> 35:37.702 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

35:37.736 --> 35:41.172 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: Carol City is just
