36:12.937 --> 36:19.377 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
PAUL SOLMAN: But Kristin
Klopfenstein, who
studies the economics of
education, worries

36:19.411 --> 36:22.981 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that, for many kids, Raise.me
