36:23.014 --> 36:25.383 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KRISTIN KLOPFENSTEIN, University
of Northern
Colorado: A lot of times, kids,
particularly

36:25.417 --> 36:31.356 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
