37:00.085 --> 37:03.521 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KRISTIN KLOPFENSTEIN: I think
those kids face
an entirely different situation,
where, when

37:03.555 --> 37:09.027 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
