raised hopes for those who might
not have

38:12.991 --> 38:14.859 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
otherwise applied.

38:14.893 --> 38:16.828 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JODY GLASSMAN, Florida
International University:
There's been so much hype. Is
the price of

38:16.861 --> 38:21.099 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
