38:21.132 --> 38:28.139 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Are you going to graduate with
all of this
debt? And Raise.me really helps
us portray

38:28.173 --> 38:31.509 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
