affordable.

38:31.543 --> 38:37.048 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: And even to the
high-achieving
students at the magnet school,
it turns out,

38:37.081 --> 38:43.454 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Raise.me has had real value.
