up even further the drive that
already spurs

38:43.488 --> 38:45.290 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
them.

38:45.323 --> 38:47.358 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUSTIN LEE: We're just always
