40:03.067 --> 40:08.973 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Venezuelan Central Bank began
printing money
at record levels, the result,
massive inflation

40:09.007 --> 40:10.975 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
in this socialist country.

40:11.009 --> 40:16.681 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The cost of consumer goods
increased 275 percent
last year, according to the
International

40:16.714 --> 40:23.421 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Monetary Fund. And that number
is expected
to double in 2016. Long lines
and empty shelves

40:23.454 --> 40:28.526 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
have come to define life for
many, as well
as anger at the Maduro
government.

40:28.559 --> 40:34.332 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In elections last year, the
opposition party
won a majority of seats in the
national Parliament.

40:34.365 --> 40:41.105 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Earlier this month, after weeks
without water,
protests erupted in this San
Cristobal neighborhood.

40:41.139 --> 40:47.378 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Meanwhile, in Caracas, nurses
protested a
lack of medicines and equipment,
while, across

40:47.412 --> 40:51.649 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
town, demonstrators called for
the president's
resignation.

40:51.683 --> 40:56.621 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And for a look at the crisis
facing Venezuela,
we welcome Scott Tong of public
radio's Marketplace.

40:56.654 --> 40:59.157 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He recently returned from a
reporting trip
there.

40:59.190 --> 41:02.927 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And Scott, I should say, was
formerly a colleague
of ours here at the "NewsHour."

41:02.960 --> 41:04.162 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, first, welcome to you,
Scott.

41:04.195 --> 41:05.029 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SCOTT TONG, Marketplace: Thanks,
Jeff.

41:05.063 --> 41:06.764 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Alright, so
Venezuela.

41:06.798 --> 41:12.203 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We hear about the impact of low
oil prices
on certain countries out there.
You saw it

41:12.236 --> 41:16.674 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
