in economic
freefall. What does that look
like?

41:16.708 --> 41:21.979 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SCOTT TONG: Oil is everything
there; 96 percent
of their export revenue comes
from oil.

41:22.013 --> 41:27.018 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
