everything
has to be imported now.

41:35.693 --> 41:41.165 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so now the price of oil has
fallen. Two
years ago, it was over $110.
It's around $40

41:41.199 --> 41:44.769 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
now. And so they don't have
dollars to import
the things. And so when you fly
there and

41:44.802 --> 41:46.037 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
you get there you, you just see
